{"tid":2498044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：積極考慮參加 2024 大選，與中國俄羅斯友好是好事可讓美國賺大錢","createTime":"2021-04-21T01:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T02:59:00.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"deabcced5e051617f6a10c10aeadb096c8040275","tid":2498044,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T01:55:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/特朗普-積極考慮參選-2024-大選-與中國俄羅斯友好是好事可讓美國賺大錢/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-2024-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8F%8B%E5%A5%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%93%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%8C%A2%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dAKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=b9416698\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E7%A9%8D%E6%A5%B5%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-2024-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8-%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%8F%8B%E5%A5%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%8B%E5%8F%AF%E8%AE%93%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B3%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%8C%A2%2F&h=70c2b784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/特朗普-積極考慮參選-2024-大選-與中國俄羅斯友好是好事可讓美國賺大錢/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統特朗普接受霍氏新聞節目 Hannity 專訪時表示，他積極研究競逐 2024 年總統大選，又說與中國、俄羅斯等國家保持友好是好事，因為可以讓美國賺大錢，而中國的問題只在於疫情（Covid 19）。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普表示，他將協助共和黨人爭取在 2022 年中期選舉中獲勝，又說自己仍然很受歡迎，民望很高，過往只要他支持哪位共和黨人，就幾乎可以篤定成功。被問到會否否於 2024 年再次問鼎白宮，特朗普說，基於法律考慮，不能直接回應，但又說自己在積極研究，又強調自己過往政績亮麗，即使下台後民望仍然高企，又說隨著時間過去，現屆拜登總統的種種問題會浮現，包括稅率會回升，各項監管會收緊，將會損害就業和經濟。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，自己在任期間要花很多精力應付「通俄門」調查，再次指摘是民主黨的政治迫害，並有損美國與俄羅斯發展友好關係，又說：「與俄羅斯友好是好事，不是壞事，與中國友好是好事，中國的問題只在於疫情」（getting along with Russia is a good thing, not a bad thing。Getting along with China is a good thing, the problem here with China was Coivd. ），「這些國家（中俄）有很多天然資源，美國原本可以賺很多錢，提升就業。」他說過去沒有一位美國總統能像自己可以從中國手上拿走那麼多錢（指美中貿易戰及對中國提高關稅），又指自己同俄羅斯總統普京感情好，「他喜歡我，我也喜歡他，這是好事，不是壞事」。他甚至說，同北韓領導人金正恩建立良好關係是有益的，因為「防止了戰爭」。"},{"pid":"4c7b94892a310ea290103a2d9b586b75f056618d","tid":2498044,"uid":155095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"蓬佩奧算啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2bd3e71e-f730-11ea-9b87-005056a964fe/w:1280/p:16x9/2020-09-14T153141Z_1499773571_RC2FYI9ZZF29_RTRMADP_3_USA-QATAR.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F2bd3e71e-f730-11ea-9b87-005056a964fe%2Fw%3A1280%2Fp%3A16x9%2F2020-09-14T153141Z_1499773571_RC2FYI9ZZF29_RTRMADP_3_USA-QATAR.webp&h=314d77cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8efd9a6e04acc5b55c7648802b1db551bcb15a45","tid":2498044,"uid":378294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:11:23.000Z","msg":"兒登仔移民去美國種票打擊支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b97a49497d18fbefaaeccf7aff4cf62dbe70279","tid":2498044,"uid":84668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:18:07.000Z","msg":"友好(笑)"},{"pid":"817b9c4365637a38584fb2bea0fac41e666b1054","tid":2498044,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"侵侵發生咩事？"},{"pid":"2c0bdb75adb7861cb9adeac59610f05b20cc5046","tid":2498044,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:19:54.000Z","msg":"可能想比pompoe 上？"},{"pid":"ce29a77f3c2daa9937a2b6faa7b699e3f6d906c2","tid":2498044,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T02:20:01.000Z","msg":"又炒車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />